# Helix CODEOWNERS
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Rules are evaluated bottom-to-top; the LAST matching pattern takes precedence.
# When a PR modifies files matching a pattern below, the specified owners are
# automatically requested for review.
#
# NOTE: When the project gains multiple contributors, replace individual
# usernames with GitHub teams (e.g., @helix-oss/maintainers,
# @helix-oss/security-reviewers, @helix-oss/devops, @helix-oss/qa).

# ============================================================================
# Default: all files require maintainer review
# ============================================================================
*                                @helix-oss

# ============================================================================
# Security-Critical Paths
# These modules handle binary format parsing, cryptographic operations,
# data integrity verification, and network transport. Changes require
# security-focused review.
# ============================================================================
src/helix/container.py           @helix-oss
src/helix/codec.py               @helix-oss
src/helix/ipfs.py                @helix-oss
src/helix/storage.py             @helix-oss
src/helix/pinning.py             @helix-oss
src/helix/errors.py              @helix-oss

# ============================================================================
# Specification & Security Documentation
# Format/design changes require both architecture and security sign-off.
# ============================================================================
docs/FORMAT.md                   @helix-oss
docs/THREAT_MODEL.md             @helix-oss
SECURITY.md                      @helix-oss

# ============================================================================
# CI / DevOps
# Workflow, build, and infrastructure changes require DevOps review.
# ============================================================================
.github/                         @helix-oss
scripts/                         @helix-oss
pyproject.toml                   @helix-oss

# ============================================================================
# Test Suite
# Security-critical tests require security reviewer.
# ============================================================================
tests/test_signature.py          @helix-oss
tests/test_encryption.py         @helix-oss
tests/test_container.py          @helix-oss
tests/                           @helix-oss

# ============================================================================
# Governance Documentation
# ============================================================================
CONTRIBUTING.md                  @helix-oss
CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md               @helix-oss
README.md                        @helix-oss
